{"title":"破冰的船——写在澳门回归的日子","authors":["颜溶"],"dates":[{"year":1999,"month":12,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"破冰的船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——写在澳门回归的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颜溶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"泊在记忆里的岛屿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在血脉的一端"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个往事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在一个世纪的冰川之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的黑暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的风雪呼啸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一百年的冬天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在中国版图北回归线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以南"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对于过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"背负着太多的耻辱和寒冷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我无法走近你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只能用自己的血取暖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我听见远处有汽笛的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呐喊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你未曾出发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却已经到达"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我撕下一页页日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又把日历"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一片片悬挂成你归航的帆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个伟大的时间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"记在一根细小的指针上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我静听"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光敲响的钟声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个世纪的冰雪消融"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"1999年12月20日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一艘破冰的船"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"归航。北回归线以南。低纬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高温。且多雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要准备一百个春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要准备好纸和笔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快乐的鼓和歌谣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要和每一位船上的亲人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻，拥抱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有止不住的泪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写给未来的期盼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在世纪之交"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在波涛之上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在太阳中央"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}